<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>ScanMyShadow — Phone Scan Report</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700;900&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --white: #FFFFFF;
    --cream: #FDFBF7;
    --ink: #111118;
    --ink-soft: #3D3D4E;
    --ink-muted: #7A7A8C;
    --gold: #B8860B;
    --gold-bright: #D4A017;
    --gold-light: #F5E6B8;
    --gold-pale: #FDF6E3;
    --red: #C0392B;
    --red-pale: #FDF0EE;
    --amber: #D35400;
    --amber-pale: #FEF5ED;
    --green: #1A7A4A;
    --green-pale: #EDF7F2;
    --border: #E8E2D5;
    --shadow-sm: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    --shadow-md: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html, body { background: var(--cream); color: var(--ink); font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
  body { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 32px 24px 60px; }

  /* HEADER */
  .report-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding-bottom: 20px; margin-bottom: 32px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border); position: relative; }
  .report-header::after { content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -2px; left: 0; width: 120px; height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold-bright), transparent); }
  .brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
  .brand img { width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--gold-light); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); object-fit: cover; }
  .brand-name { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--ink); letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .brand-name span { color: var(--gold); }
  .report-meta { text-align: right; }
  .report-type { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .report-date { font-size: 11.5px; color: var(--ink-muted); margin-top: 3px; font-weight: 500; }

  /* CONFIDENTIAL */
  .confidential-bar { background: var(--gold-pale); border: 1px solid var(--gold-light); border-radius: 8px; padding: 9px 16px; margin-bottom: 28px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-size: 11.5px; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .confidential-bar::before { content: '🔐'; font-size: 14px; }

  /* HERO */
  .hero { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-top: 3px solid var(--gold-bright); border-radius: 16px; padding: 36px 32px 32px; margin-bottom: 24px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); text-align: center; }
  .hero-subject { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .hero-phone { font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .hero-headline { font-size: 15px; color: var(--ink-soft); max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto 24px; line-height: 1.65; }
  .hero-headline strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 700; }
  .severity-badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .severity-badge.high { background: var(--red-pale); color: var(--red); border: 1.5px solid rgba(192,57,43,0.25); }
  .severity-badge.medium { background: var(--amber-pale); color: var(--amber); border: 1.5px solid rgba(211,84,0,0.22); }
  .severity-badge.low { background: var(--green-pale); color: var(--green); border: 1.5px solid rgba(26,122,74,0.22); }
  .severity-dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .severity-badge.high .severity-dot { background: var(--red); }
  .severity-badge.medium .severity-dot { background: var(--amber); }
  .stat-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 14px; margin-top: 8px; }
  .stat-card { background: var(--cream); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 18px 12px; text-align: center; }
  .stat-card.accent { border-color: var(--gold-light); background: var(--gold-pale); }
  .stat-card.danger { border-color: rgba(192,57,43,0.20); background: var(--red-pale); }
  .stat-number { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 36px; font-weight: 900; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 6px; color: var(--ink); }
  .stat-card.accent .stat-number { color: var(--gold); }
  .stat-card.danger .stat-number { color: var(--red); }
  .stat-label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink-muted); letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-transform: uppercase; }

  /* NARRATIVE */
  .narrative-box { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-left: 4px solid var(--gold-bright); border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); }
  .narrative-label { font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .narrative-text { font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.75; }

  /* INFO NOTE */
  .info-note { background: #F4F6FF; border: 1px solid rgba(70,90,200,0.14); border-radius: 10px; padding: 14px 18px; margin-bottom: 24px; display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: flex-start; }
  .info-note-icon { font-size: 15px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
  .info-note-body { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.65; }
  .info-note-body strong { color: var(--ink); }

  /* SECTION */
  .section { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 20px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); }
  .section-header { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 18px 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--cream); }
  .section-title-group { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
  .section-icon { width: 34px; height: 34px; border-radius: 9px; background: var(--gold-pale); border: 1px solid var(--gold-light); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .section-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); }
  .section-subtitle { font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink-muted); margin-top: 2px; font-weight: 500; }
  .section-count { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold); background: var(--gold-pale); border: 1px solid var(--gold-light); padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 999px; }
  .section-count.danger { color: var(--red); background: var(--red-pale); border-color: rgba(192,57,43,0.20); }
  .section-body { padding: 20px 24px; }

  /* DIGITAL SHADOW */
  .shadow-section { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 20px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); }
  .shadow-strip { padding: 14px 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 14px; }
  .shadow-strip:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .shadow-strip-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.09em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); flex: 0 0 110px; padding-top: 2px; }
  .shadow-pills { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; }
  .shadow-pill { font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink); background: var(--cream); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 6px; padding: 4px 10px; font-weight: 500; }
  .shadow-pill.icon-pill { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; padding: 4px 10px 4px 6px; }
  .shadow-kv { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; width: 100%; }
  .shadow-kv-row { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 8px; font-size: 12.5px; line-height: 1.5; }
  .shadow-kv-label { font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; flex: 0 0 110px; padding-top: 1px; }
  .shadow-kv-value { color: var(--ink-soft); word-break: break-all; }

  /* PLATFORM ROWS */
  .platform-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 42px minmax(120px, 170px) 1fr; align-items: flex-start; padding: 16px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); gap: 14px; page-break-inside: avoid; break-inside: avoid; }
  .platform-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .platform-icon { width: 38px; height: 38px; border-radius: 10px; background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); overflow: hidden; }
  .platform-icon img { width: 26px; height: 26px; object-fit: contain; display: block; }
  .platform-name { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); padding-top: 8px; }
  .platform-detail-wrap { flex: 1; position: relative; }
  .platform-summary { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 5px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .evidence-chip { font-size: 10.5px; color: var(--ink-soft); background: var(--cream); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 5px; padding: 3px 7px; line-height: 1.35; }
  .evidence-chip strong { color: var(--gold); font-size: 9.5px; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-right: 3px; }
  .platform-evidence { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 6px 10px; padding: 10px 12px; background: var(--cream); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; }
  .evidence-row { min-width: 0; font-size: 11.5px; line-height: 1.45; }
  .evidence-label { display: block; font-size: 9.5px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 1px; }
  .evidence-value { color: var(--ink-soft); word-break: break-word; }

  /* BREACH ROWS */
  .breach-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 8px minmax(130px, 190px) 1fr; align-items: flex-start; padding: 16px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); gap: 14px; page-break-inside: avoid; break-inside: avoid; }
  .breach-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .breach-sev { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 14px; }
  .breach-sev.high { background: var(--red); }
  .breach-sev.medium { background: var(--amber); }
  .breach-name { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); }
  .breach-meta { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; margin-top: 6px; }
  .breach-meta span { font-size: 10.5px; color: var(--ink-muted); background: var(--cream); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 5px; padding: 2px 7px; }
  .breach-content { min-width: 0; }
  .breach-description { font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink-soft); margin-bottom: 6px; line-height: 1.6; }
  .breach-data-list { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 4px; }
  .breach-data-list span { font-size: 10px; background: var(--red-pale); color: var(--red); border: 1px solid rgba(192,57,43,0.15); border-radius: 4px; padding: 2px 7px; font-weight: 500; }
  .breach-sev-badge { font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 700; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 999px; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-transform: uppercase; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .breach-sev-badge.high { background: var(--red-pale); color: var(--red); }
  .breach-sev-badge.medium { background: var(--amber-pale); color: var(--amber); }
  .breach-sev-badge.low { background: var(--green-pale); color: var(--green); }

  /* TIMELINE */
  .timeline-section { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 20px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); }
  .timeline-headline-box { padding: 24px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--cream); }
  .timeline-headline-number { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 42px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--gold); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .timeline-headline-text { font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-soft); font-weight: 500; }
  .timeline-fake-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .timeline-fake-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .tl-date { font-weight: 700; font-size: 11px; color: var(--gold); width: 72px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .tl-source { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); width: 110px; flex-shrink: 0; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; }
  .tl-content { font-size: 11.5px; color: var(--ink-soft); overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; }

  /* DIVIDER */
  .gold-divider { height: 1px; margin: 28px 0; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold-bright), var(--gold-light), transparent); }

  /* SOURCES */
  .source-chip { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; background: var(--cream); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 6px 10px; }
  .source-chip img { width: 18px; height: 18px; object-fit: contain; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .source-chip-name { font-size: 11.5px; color: var(--ink-soft); font-weight: 500; }

  /* ACTION CARD */
  .action-card {
    page-break-before: always;
    break-before: always;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, #fffdf7 0%, #fdf6e3 100%);
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(201,154,58,0.30);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 40px 36px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(201,154,58,0.14), 0 2px 8px rgba(20,21,26,0.05);
  }
  .action-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #a67922, #d4a017, #f3cf74, #d4a017, #a67922);
  }
  .action-card-icon { font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .action-card-headline {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #14151a;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .action-card-sub {
    font-size: 13.5px;
    color: #343843;
    max-width: 460px;
    margin: 0 auto 22px;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .action-card-sub strong { color: #14151a; }
  .action-btn-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 14px;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .action-btn-primary {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, #FFD000, #F5A800 50%, #E08C00);
    color: #1A0F00;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 900;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(245,168,0,0.45), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
  }
  .action-btn-secondary {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(201,154,58,0.45);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #14151a;
    text-decoration: none;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(201,154,58,0.12);
  }

  /* GUIDE / REMOVAL TOOLKIT */
  .guide-section { margin-top: 32px; }
  .guide-section-header { border-left: 4px solid var(--gold-bright); padding: 14px 18px; background: var(--gold-pale); border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .guide-section-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .guide-section-sub { font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--ink-soft); }
  .tip-card { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px 18px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); page-break-inside: avoid; break-inside: avoid; }
  .tip-num { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.10em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .tip-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 5px; }
  .tip-body { font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.65; }
  .tip-body ol { padding-left: 18px; margin-top: 4px; }
  .tip-body ol li { margin-bottom: 5px; }

  /* FOOTER */
  .report-footer { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 20px; text-align: center; }
  .footer-main { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--ink-soft); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .footer-conf { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .footer-text { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(17,17,24,0.72); line-height: 1.7; }
  .footer-id { font-size: 10px; color: rgba(17,17,24,0.63); margin-top: 6px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }

  /* PAGE BREAKS */
  .page-break { page-break-after: always; break-after: always; }
  .no-break { page-break-inside: avoid; break-inside: avoid; }

  @media print {
    body { background: white; padding: 0; }
    @page { margin: 24px; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    body { padding: 16px 14px 40px; }
    .stat-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .stat-row .stat-card:last-child { grid-column: 1/-1; }
    .hero { padding: 24px 20px; }
    .section-body { padding: 16px; }
    .platform-row { grid-template-columns: 42px 1fr; }
    .platform-name { padding-top: 0; }
    .platform-detail-wrap { grid-column: 1/-1; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HEADER -->
<header class="report-header">
  <div class="brand">
    <img src="{{ brand_logo_uri }}" alt="ScanMyShadow" onerror="this.style.background='#F5E6B8';this.style.borderRadius='12px'">
    <div>
      <div class="brand-name">Scan<span>My</span>Shadow</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="report-meta">
    <div class="report-type">₹998 Privacy Scan — Phone Deep Dive</div>
    <div class="report-date">{{ report_date }}</div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- CONFIDENTIAL -->
<div class="confidential-bar">Confidential &nbsp;·&nbsp; Do not share</div>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-subject">Phone Number Scanned</div>
  <div class="hero-phone">{{ phone_number }}</div>
  <div class="hero-headline">We searched the entire internet for your phone number.<br><strong>Here is what we found.</strong></div>
  {% if breach_count == 0 %}
  <div class="severity-badge low">Low Risk — No Data Breaches Found</div>
  {% elsif breach_count == 1 %}
  <div class="severity-badge medium"><span class="severity-dot"></span>Medium Risk — Attention Recommended</div>
  {% else %}
  <div class="severity-badge high"><span class="severity-dot"></span>High Risk — Immediate Attention Needed</div>
  {% endif %}
  <div class="stat-row">
    <div class="stat-card accent"><div class="stat-number">{{ platform_count }}</div><div class="stat-label">Platforms Found</div></div>
    <div class="stat-card danger"><div class="stat-number">{{ breach_count }}</div><div class="stat-label">Data Breaches</div></div>
    <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-number">{{ years_of_history }}</div><div class="stat-label">Years of History</div></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- NARRATIVE -->
<div class="narrative-box">
  <div class="narrative-label">Our Finding</div>
  <div class="narrative-text">{{ narrative }}</div>
</div>

<!-- INFO NOTE -->
<div class="info-note">
  <div class="info-note-icon">ℹ️</div>
  <div class="info-note-body"><strong>A note before you continue.</strong> Not every result is a red flag. Platforms you use daily — WhatsApp, Truecaller, Google — will always appear. Pay attention to <strong>entries from services you don't recognise or no longer use.</strong> Those are the ones that matter most.</div>
</div>

<!-- DIGITAL SHADOW -->
<div class="shadow-section" style="page-break-before:always;break-before:always;">
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="section-title-group">
      <div class="section-icon">🪞</div>
      <div>
        <div class="section-title">Your Digital Shadow</div>
        <div class="section-subtitle">Identity data found linked to this phone number</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-count">{{ identity_count }} attributes</div>
  </div>

  <!-- Scan Stats -->
  <div style="padding:12px 24px;background:var(--cream);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px 20px;">
    <span style="font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.09em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);flex:0 0 100%;margin-bottom:2px;">Scan Stats</span>
    <span style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);"><strong style="color:var(--gold);">{{ stats.registered_modules }}</strong> platforms registered</span>
    <span style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);"><strong style="color:var(--red);">{{ stats.breached_modules }}</strong> breach sources checked</span>
    <span style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);"><strong style="color:var(--ink);">{{ stats.caller_id_entries }}</strong> caller ID entries</span>
    <span style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);"><strong style="color:var(--ink);">{{ stats.unique_names }}</strong> name variants</span>
    <span style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);"><strong style="color:var(--ink);">{{ stats.unique_usernames }}</strong> username variants</span>
    <span style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);"><strong style="color:var(--ink);">{{ stats.total_events }}</strong> timeline events</span>
  </div>

  <!-- Names -->
  <div class="shadow-strip">
    <div class="shadow-strip-label">Names Found</div>
    <div class="shadow-pills">{% for name in identity_names %}<div class="shadow-pill">{{ name }}</div>{% endfor %}</div>
  </div>

  <!-- Usernames -->
  {% if identity_usernames.size > 0 %}
  <div class="shadow-strip">
    <div class="shadow-strip-label">Usernames</div>
    <div class="shadow-pills">{% for username in identity_usernames %}<div class="shadow-pill">{{ username }}</div>{% endfor %}</div>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  <!-- Caller ID Entries -->
  {% if caller_id_entries.size > 0 %}
  <div class="shadow-strip" style="page-break-inside:avoid;break-inside:avoid;">
    <div class="shadow-strip-label">Caller ID</div>
    <div class="shadow-kv">
      {% for entry in caller_id_entries %}
      <div class="shadow-kv-row">
        <span class="shadow-kv-label">{{ entry.app_name }}</span>
        <span class="shadow-kv-value">{% if entry.display_name != "" %}{{ entry.display_name }}{% endif %}{% if entry.tag != "" %} · <em>{{ entry.tag }}</em>{% endif %}</span>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  <!-- Account Hints -->
  {% if account_hints.size > 0 %}
  <div class="shadow-strip" style="page-break-inside:avoid;break-inside:avoid;">
    <div class="shadow-strip-label">Account Hints</div>
    <div class="shadow-kv">
      {% for hint in account_hints %}
      <div class="shadow-kv-row">
        <span class="shadow-kv-label">{{ hint.source }}</span>
        <span class="shadow-kv-value">{{ hint.value }}{% if hint.explain != "" %} — <em style="color:var(--ink-muted);">{{ hint.explain }}</em>{% endif %}</span>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  <!-- Also On -->
  {% if also_registered.size > 0 %}
  <div class="shadow-strip" style="page-break-inside:avoid;break-inside:avoid;">
    <div class="shadow-strip-label">Also On</div>
    <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:7px;">
      {% for item in also_registered %}
      <div class="shadow-pill icon-pill">
        <img src="https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain={{ item | downcase | remove: ' ' }}.com&sz=32" alt="{{ item }}" style="width:16px;height:16px;object-fit:contain;" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
        {{ item }}
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endif %}
</div>

<!-- PLATFORMS — Where Your Number Was Found -->
<div class="section" style="page-break-before:always;break-before:always;">
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="section-title-group">
      <div class="section-icon">📱</div>
      <div>
        <div class="section-title">Where Your Number Was Found</div>
        <div class="section-subtitle">Apps and websites that have your phone number</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-count">{{ platform_count }} found</div>
  </div>
  <div class="section-body">
    {% for platform in platforms %}
    <div class="platform-row">
      <div class="platform-icon">
        <img src="{{ platform.logo_uri }}" alt="{{ platform.name }}" width="26" height="26" style="object-fit:contain;border-radius:3px;" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
      </div>
      <div class="platform-name">{{ platform.name }}</div>
      <div class="platform-detail-wrap">
        <div class="platform-summary">
          {% for field in platform.fields %}{% if forloop.index <= 4 %}<span class="evidence-chip"><strong>{{ field.label }}</strong>{{ field.value }}</span>{% endif %}{% endfor %}
        </div>
        <div class="platform-evidence">
          {% for field in platform.fields %}
          <div class="evidence-row"><span class="evidence-label">{{ field.label }}</span><span class="evidence-value">{{ field.value }}</span></div>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>

<!-- BREACHES -->
<div class="section" style="page-break-before:always;break-before:always;">
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="section-title-group">
      <div class="section-icon">⚠️</div>
      <div>
        <div class="section-title">Data Breaches</div>
        <div class="section-subtitle">Your data was leaked in these incidents</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-count danger">{{ breach_count }} found</div>
  </div>
  <div class="section-body">
    {% for breach in breaches %}
    <div class="breach-row">
      <div class="breach-sev {{ breach.severity }}"></div>
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;">
        <div style="width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--white);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;overflow:hidden;"><img src="{{ breach.logo_uri }}" alt="{{ breach.name }}" style="width:20px;height:20px;object-fit:contain;" onerror="this.style.display='none'"></div>
        <div>
          <div class="breach-name">{{ breach.name }}</div>
          <div class="breach-meta">
            <span>{{ breach.date }}</span>
            <span>{{ breach.records }} records</span>
            <span class="breach-sev-badge {{ breach.severity }}">{% if breach.severity == "high" %}High Risk{% elsif breach.severity == "medium" %}Medium Risk{% else %}Low Risk{% endif %}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="breach-content">
        <div class="breach-description">{{ breach.description }}{% if breach.website != "" %} <span style="color:var(--ink-muted);">Website: {{ breach.website }}</span>{% endif %}</div>
        {% if breach.breached_data.size > 0 %}
        <div class="breach-data-list">{% for bd in breach.breached_data %}<span>{{ bd }}</span>{% endfor %}</div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
    {% if breach_count == 0 %}
    <div style="padding:16px 0 6px;text-align:center;">
      <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--green);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px;">✓ No breaches found on record</div>
      <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-muted);line-height:1.6;">Your phone number was not found in any known data breach databases. Breaches can take months to surface, so a clean result today does not guarantee one tomorrow.</div>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</div>

<!-- TIMELINE -->
<div class="timeline-section" style="page-break-before:always;break-before:always;">
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="section-title-group">
      <div class="section-icon">🕐</div>
      <div>
        <div class="section-title">Your Digital Timeline</div>
        <div class="section-subtitle">A history of where your phone data has appeared</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="timeline-headline-box">
    <div class="timeline-headline-number">{{ years_of_history }} years</div>
    <div class="timeline-headline-text">Your phone number has been active online since <strong>{{ earliest_year }}</strong> — that is {{ total_events }} events we tracked across different platforms.</div>
  </div>
  {% if year_groups.size > 0 %}
  <div style="padding:16px 24px 0;">
    <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.09em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:10px;">Activity by Year</div>
    {% assign max_count = 1 %}
    {% for yg in year_groups %}{% if yg.count > max_count %}{% assign max_count = yg.count %}{% endif %}{% endfor %}
    <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:6px;height:64px;">
      {% for yg in year_groups %}
      {% assign bar_pct = yg.count | times: 100 | divided_by: max_count %}
      <div style="flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:2px;">
        <div style="font-size:8.5px;color:var(--ink-muted);font-weight:600;">{{ yg.count }}</div>
        <div style="width:100%;background:var(--gold-bright);border-radius:3px 3px 0 0;height:{{ bar_pct | times: 44 | divided_by: 100 | plus: 4 }}px;min-height:4px;"></div>
        <div style="font-size:8px;color:var(--ink-muted);font-weight:500;writing-mode:vertical-rl;transform:rotate(180deg);height:26px;line-height:1;">{{ yg.year }}</div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endif %}
  <div style="padding:16px 24px;">
    {% for event in events %}
    <div class="timeline-fake-row">
      <div class="tl-date">{{ event.date }}</div>
      <div class="tl-source">{{ event.source }}</div>
      <div class="tl-content">{{ event.content }}</div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>

<div class="gold-divider"></div>

<!-- SOURCES CHECKED -->
<div class="section" style="margin-bottom:20px;page-break-before:always;break-before:always;">
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="section-title-group">
      <div class="section-icon">🔍</div>
      <div>
        <div class="section-title">Sources Checked</div>
        <div class="section-subtitle">Every database and platform we scanned</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section-body">
    <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:7px;align-items:center;">
      {% for src in sources_with_logos %}
      <div class="source-chip">
        {% if src.locked %}<span style="font-size:12px;">🔓</span>{% else %}<img src="{{ src.logo_uri }}" alt="{{ src.name }}" style="width:18px;height:18px;object-fit:contain;">{% endif %}
        <span class="source-chip-name">{{ src.name }}</span>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
      <div style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--ink-muted);font-style:italic;padding:5px 4px;">+ many more</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- REMOVAL TOOLKIT + PRIVACY GUIDE -->
<div class="guide-section" style="page-break-before:always;break-before:always;">
  <div class="guide-section-header" style="page-break-after:avoid;break-after:avoid;">
    <div class="guide-section-title">Your Personalised Removal Toolkit</div>
    <div class="guide-section-sub">Step-by-step actions specific to your scan results.</div>
  </div>
  {{ removal_toolkit }}

  <div class="guide-section-header" style="margin-top:32px;page-break-before:always;break-before:always;">
    <div class="guide-section-title">Your Privacy Protection Guide</div>
    <div class="guide-section-sub">Steps to take right now to reduce your exposure.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="tip-card no-break"><div class="tip-num">Tip 01</div><div class="tip-title">Change your phone-linked account passwords immediately</div><div class="tip-body">Start with your bank, UPI apps (PhonePe, GPay, Paytm), and email. Your phone number is often used for OTP-based login — if it is leaked, these accounts are at risk.</div></div>
  <div class="tip-card no-break"><div class="tip-num">Tip 02</div><div class="tip-title">Turn on two-factor authentication (2FA)</div><div class="tip-body">Enable 2FA on all major apps — even with a leaked number, a second verification step blocks unauthorised access. Use an authenticator app where possible, not just SMS.</div></div>
  <div class="tip-card no-break"><div class="tip-num">Tip 03</div><div class="tip-title">Watch out for SIM swap fraud</div><div class="tip-body">Scammers can call your telecom operator and transfer your number to a new SIM — then receive your OTPs. Call your operator (Jio, Airtel, Vi) and ask to lock your SIM against swaps.</div></div>
  <div class="tip-card no-break"><div class="tip-num">Tip 04</div><div class="tip-title">Do not answer calls from unknown or international numbers</div><div class="tip-body">Once your number is in breach databases, it gets sold to scammers. Calls from +1, +44, +92 with urgent messages about bank accounts or parcels are almost always fraud.</div></div>
  <div class="tip-card no-break"><div class="tip-num">Tip 05</div><div class="tip-title">Check which apps are linked to your phone number</div><div class="tip-body">Go through your apps — food delivery, travel, shopping — and remove your number from any app you no longer use. The fewer places it appears, the safer you are.</div></div>
  <div class="tip-card no-break"><div class="tip-num">Tip 06</div><div class="tip-title">Use a separate number for app registrations</div><div class="tip-body">Consider getting a second SIM or using a virtual number just for signing up to apps and websites. Keep your primary number private.</div></div>
  <div class="tip-card no-break"><div class="tip-num">Tip 07</div><div class="tip-title">Register on the DND (Do Not Disturb) list</div><div class="tip-body">Text START DND to 1909 or use the TRAI DND app to reduce unsolicited calls and messages. It will not stop all spam, but reduces it significantly.</div></div>
  <div class="tip-card no-break"><div class="tip-num">Tip 08</div><div class="tip-title">Scan again in 90 days</div><div class="tip-body">Breaches are discovered months after they happen. A clean result today does not guarantee clean results tomorrow. Book your next scan at scanmyshadow.com.</div></div>
</div>

